    "text": {
      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/People\" title=\"People\">People</a> * Daniel José Queraltó</b>\n</p>\n<div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:162px;\"><a href=\"https://ratings.fide.com/card.phtml?event=6900089\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"/images/7/7c/JoseQueraltoDaniel.jpg\" width=\"160\" height=\"200\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:JoseQueraltoDaniel.jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div>Daniel José Queraltó <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div> \n<p><b>Daniel José Queraltó</b>,<br />\nan Andorran computer scientist and <a href=\"/FIDE\" title=\"FIDE\">FIDE</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Candidate_Master#Candidate_Master_.28CM.29\">Candidate Master</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-2\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup> in chess. He is promoter of the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Catalan_language\">Catalan</a> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ca.wikipedia.org/wiki/Portada\">Wikipedia</a>, specially on topics related to chess, mathematics and computer science, and has featured its first article about the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Abacus\">Abacus</a> on March 17, 2001 <sup id=\"cite_ref-3\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup> <sup id=\"cite_ref-4\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-4\">&#91;4&#93;</a></sup>. For his contributions he received the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ca.wikipedia.org/wiki/Llu%C3%ADs_Carulla_i_Canals\">Lluís Carulla</a> award in 2013 <sup id=\"cite_ref-5\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-5\">&#91;5&#93;</a></sup>. As computer chess programmer, Daniel José is author of the <a href=\"/UCI\" title=\"UCI\">UCI</a> compliant chess engine <a href=\"/Andscacs\" title=\"Andscacs\">Andscacs</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-6\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-6\">&#91;6&#93;</a></sup>. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Chess_Olympiads\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess Olympiads</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Forum_Posts\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Posts</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#2014\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2014</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#2015_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2015 ...</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#2020_...\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">2020 ...</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Chess_Olympiads\">Chess Olympiads</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Jos%C3%A9_Queralt%C3%B3&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" title=\"Edit section: Chess Olympiads\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<p>Daniel José Queraltó represented <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Andorra\">Andorra</a> at eleven <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Chess_Olympiad\">Chess Olympiads</a> so far. Similar to Papua New Guinean player and chess programmer <a href=\"/Shaun_Press\" title=\"Shaun Press\">Shaun Press</a>, he was quite close to his computer chess fellows at the <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/37th_Chess_Olympiad\">37th Chess Olympiad</a> in <a href=\"/WCCC_2006\" title=\"WCCC 2006\">Turin 2006</a>.\n</p>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Forum_Posts\">Forum Posts</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Jos%C3%A9_Queralt%C3%B3&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" title=\"Edit section: Forum Posts\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2014\">2014</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Jos%C3%A9_Queralt%C3%B3&amp;action=edit&amp;section=3\" title=\"Edit section: 2014\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51182\">New engine - Andscacs</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel José Queraltó</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 06, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51306&amp;start=4\">Re: Accelerated Move Gen in Null Move</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel José Queraltó</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 17, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51383\">testing procedure</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel José Queraltó</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 23, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/Engine_Testing\" title=\"Engine Testing\">Engine Testing</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51475\">Andscacs - New version</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel José Queraltó</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, March 03, 2014</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=51992\">Idea of different history</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel José Queraltó</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 14, 2014&#160;» <a href=\"/History_Heuristic\" title=\"History Heuristic\">History Heuristic</a></li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2015_...\">2015 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Jos%C3%A9_Queralt%C3%B3&amp;action=edit&amp;section=4\" title=\"Edit section: 2015 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=55970\">Trying to improve lazy smp</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel José Queraltó</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, April 11, 2015&#160;» <a href=\"/Lazy_SMP\" title=\"Lazy SMP\">Lazy SMP</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=61942\">King Indian like and usefulness of engines</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel José Queraltó</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, November 03, 2016</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=63911\">advanced krkp function</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel José Queraltó</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, May 06, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Rook_Endgame\" title=\"Rook Endgame\">Rook Endgame</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64242\">Fastest pawn quiet move generation I was able to come with</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel José Queraltó</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 10, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/C#Duff\" title=\"C\">Duff's Device</a>, <a href=\"/Move_Generation\" title=\"Move Generation\">Move Generation</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64274\">Hash table</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel José Queraltó</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, June 12, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Transposition Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64522\">Improving hash replacing schema for analysis mode</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel José Queraltó</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 05, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Transposition_Table#ReplacementStrategies\" title=\"Transposition Table\">Replacement Strategy</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum/viewtopic.php?t=64720\">Stockfish version with hash saving capability</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel José Queraltó</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, July 25, 2017&#160;» <a href=\"/Stockfish\" title=\"Stockfish\">Stockfish</a>, <a href=\"/Persistent_Hash_Table\" title=\"Persistent Hash Table\">Persistent Hash Table</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=69302\">Andscacs - New version 0.95</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel José Queraltó</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, December 17, 2018</li></ul>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"2020_...\">2020 ...</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Jos%C3%A9_Queralt%C3%B3&amp;action=edit&amp;section=5\" title=\"Edit section: 2020 ...\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=73096&amp;start=6\">Re: Andscacs</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel José Queraltó</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, February 15, 2020</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.talkchess.com/forum3/viewtopic.php?f=2&amp;t=75218\">Remote UCI</a> by <a class=\"mw-selflink selflink\">Daniel José Queraltó</a>, <a href=\"/CCC\" title=\"CCC\">CCC</a>, September 26, 2020</li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"External_Links\">External Links</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Jos%C3%A9_Queralt%C3%B3&amp;action=edit&amp;section=6\" title=\"Edit section: External Links\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<ul><li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://ca.wikipedia.org/wiki/Daniel_Jos%C3%A9_Queralt%C3%B3\">Daniel José Queraltó - Viquipèdia, l'enciclopèdia lliure</a> (<a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Catalan_language\">Catalan</a>)</li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ratings.fide.com/card.phtml?event=6900089\">Jose Queralto, Daniel FIDE Chess Profile - Players Arbiters Trainers</a></li>\n<li> <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chessgames.com/player/daniel_jose_queralto.html\">The chess games of Daniel Jose Queralto</a> from <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.chessgames.com/index.html\">chessgames.com</a></li></ul>\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"References\">References</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Daniel_Jos%C3%A9_Queralt%C3%B3&amp;action=edit&amp;section=7\" title=\"Edit section: References\">edit</a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h1>\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-1\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ratings.fide.com/card.phtml?event=6900089\">Jose Queralto, Daniel FIDE Chess Profile - Players Arbiters Trainers</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-2\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-2\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ratings.fide.com/card.phtml?event=6900089\">Jose Queralto, Daniel FIDE Chess Profile - Players Arbiters Trainers</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-3\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-3\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ca.wikipedia.org/wiki/Viquip%C3%A8dia:Notes_de_premsa/10_anys_amb_la_Viquip%C3%A8dia\">Viquipèdia:Notes de premsa/La Viquipèdia en català convida a tothom a celebrar el desè aniversari - wikipedia.ca</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-4\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ca.wikipedia.org/wiki/%C3%80bac\">Àbac - Wikipedia.ca</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-5\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-5\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://www.bondia.ad/cultura/premi-actuacio-civica-limpulsor-de-la-viquipedia-landorra-daniel-jose\">Premi Actuació Cívica per a l’impulsor de la Viquipèdia, l’andorrà Daniel José | Diari digital d'Andorra BonDia</a></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-6\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-6\">↑</a></spa